{"header":"<h1>Module type <code><span>Memory_sig.Offset_to_Scalar</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":true,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"codex","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Domains","href":"../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Memory_sig","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Offset_to_Scalar","href":"#","kind":"module-type"}],"toc":[],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"<p>Offset is above Scalar on the domain stack, so we decompose a Offset stack in a Scalar stack and a context: <code>Lift.ctx address_ctx = (scalar_ctx,f)</code> means that <code>f scalar_ctx = address_ctx_ctx</code>.</p>","content":"<div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Offset\"><a href=\"#module-Offset\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"Offset/index.html\">Offset</a></span><span> : <a href=\"../module-type-Offset/index.html\">Offset</a></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Scalar\"><a href=\"#module-Scalar\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"Scalar/index.html\">Scalar</a></span><span> : <a href=\"../../Domain_sig/module-type-Base/index.html\">Domain_sig.Base</a></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-ctx\"><a href=\"#val-ctx\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> ctx : \u000A  <span><a href=\"Offset/Context/index.html#type-t\">Offset.Context.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <a href=\"Scalar/Context/index.html#type-t\">Scalar.Context.t</a> * <span>(<span><a href=\"Scalar/Context/index.html#type-t\">Scalar.Context.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <a href=\"Scalar/Context/index.html#type-t\">Scalar.Context.t</a>)</span></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-serialize_binary\"><a href=\"#val-serialize_binary\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> serialize_binary : \u000A  <span><span class=\"label\">widens</span>:bool <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span class=\"label\">size</span>:int <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><a href=\"Offset/Context/index.html#type-t\">Offset.Context.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><a href=\"Scalar/index.html#type-binary\">Scalar.binary</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><a href=\"Offset/Context/index.html#type-t\">Offset.Context.t</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><a href=\"Scalar/index.html#type-binary\">Scalar.binary</a> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'a</span> <a href=\"Offset/Context/index.html#type-in_acc\">Offset.Context.in_acc</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span>\u000A  <span><span>(<a href=\"Scalar/index.html#type-binary\">Scalar.binary</a>, <span class=\"type-var\">'a</span>)</span> <a href=\"Offset/Context/index.html#type-result\">Offset.Context.result</a></span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Allows serialization of a Scalar.binary in a Offset domain.</p></div></div>"}